&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;이미지는 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;다음사전에서 가져왔습니다 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://alldic.daum.net/search.do?q=%EC%B0%A1%EC%BD%94&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;http://alldic.daum.net/search.do?q=%EC%B0%A1%EC%BD%94&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
